All right.

54
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,040
I'll keep my distance from him.

55
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:29,920
Dad.

56
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,560
I'd like to talk to you.

57
00:03:36,817 --> 00:03:37,760
I'm sorry, Dad.

58
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:41,240
I know you found it surprising

59
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:43,080
that Yu and I were together.

60
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:46,440
After all, I'm working at Shengyue,

61
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:47,920
and I'm your adopted daughter.

62
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:50,600
It may have some impact on the company.

63
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:54,400
Here you go.

64
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:03,400
What is this?

65
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:06,240
I will announce to the public
that I'm no longer your adopted daughter,

66
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,640
and I will leave Shengyue.

67
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,080
But

68
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:11,760
Yu and I truly love each other.

69
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,760
I don't want to leave him.

70
00:04:15,399 --> 00:04:16,359
