72
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:20,280
I disagree with you leaving
the Bai family,

73
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,920
leaving Shengyue,

74
00:04:22,280 --> 00:04:23,880
and being with Yu.

75
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,800
