92
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:01,040
And I had to marry with the Yun family.

93
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,160
So I gave you to my best friends,

94
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,480
the Xu couple.

95
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,480
After Xu An and his wife
had an accident,

96
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:11,200
I brought you back to the Bai family

97
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,760
under the guise of adoption.

98
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:13,800
Why didn't you

99
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,360
